description: Urban Bumpkin BBQ is a modern rolling cuisine that combines Asian, Native Alaskan and Russian dishes with American smoking traditions and unique bang'n flavors, some may call it the idenity crisis menu but it's defintely the epitome of melting pot 'Murica! All meats are rubbed with an Urban Bumpkin special spice blend and smoked for up to 12 hours over wood fire until deliciously  tender and juicy!
name: Urban Bumpkin BBQ
